  "name": "RPlog_Battle_of_Teyr_Part_3",
  "title": "The Fall of Teyr Rift",
  "summary": "The Empire launches its ground assault on the resistance's final stronghold in the Teyr Rift, with AT-ATs and stormtroopers advancing under cover of Dante's bomber wing. Anti-aircraft fire takes a heavy toll, shooting down both bomber pilot Odion and Interceptor pilot Marz Tanik, who eject behind enemy lines while their squadron duels reinforcing resistance TIEs overhead. On the ground, stormtrooper Illyana and her squad under Sergeant Dill breach a resistance gate to rescue the two stranded pilots, sparking a running firefight as the Imperials close in. The resistance command center is found abandoned, its leaders escaping by shuttle, while the last defenders surrender to Illyana; Odion and Marz hole up in an escape pod awaiting their rescuers as the battle ends with Teyr fallen but the rebel leadership still at large.",
